('DOC-068', 'Renewal Playbook', 'Save Play: Customer Advisory Board Invitation for Strategic Accounts', 'West', 'Enterprise', 'ALL ACCOUNTS',
 '2026-06-15',
 'RENEWAL PLAYBOOK: Customer Advisory Board (CAB) Invitation. Strategy: Invite at-risk West Enterprise accounts to join a newly formed Customer Advisory Board focused on platform reliability. Purpose: (1) Demonstrate that customer voice directly influences product roadmap. (2) Create executive-level engagement touchpoint beyond commercial relationship. (3) Build community among customers with shared reliability concerns - they reassure each other once improvements are visible. (4) Provide early access to new reliability features, creating switching cost. Target candidates: Top 10 West Enterprise accounts by ARR with renewal risk >70. Specifically: Acme Financial Services, TechNova Solutions, Pacific Mutual Insurance, NovaPay Financial, Western Digital Analytics, Redwood Capital Management, Summit Analytics Group, Velocity Logistics, Pinnacle Biotech, Cascade Health Systems. Offer: quarterly in-person meetings (hosted at our HQ), direct access to VP Engineering and CTO, input on reliability roadmap prioritization, first access to new infrastructure options. Budget: $200K annually for events and travel. Expected ROI: retaining even 2 of the top-10 accounts covers 5+ years of CAB costs.'),

('DOC-069', 'Exec Escalation', 'ESCALATION: NovaPay Financial - Renewal in 2 Days, Dedicated Compute Delivery', 'West', 'Enterprise', 'NovaPay Financial',
 '2026-06-13',
